      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if they can just opt out of anything they don't like, doesn't that basically create a second set of rules for certain groups? like, if a law is meant to protect public health or civil rights for everyone, doesn't letting religious groups skip it actually end up hurting the people who don't have those exemptions? it feels like it's creating inequality under the law.",
